  一个正定不等式的最佳参数
  A Sharp Parameter Value of a Positive Definite Inequality
 
</article-title></title-group><contrib-group><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>冯</surname><given-names>贝叶</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff1"><sub>1</sub></xref><xref ref-type="corresp" rid="cor1"><sup>*</sup></xref></contrib></contrib-group><aff id="aff1"><label>1</label><addr-line>中国科学院应用数学研究所，北京</addr-line></aff><author-notes><corresp id="cor1">* E-mail:<email>fby@amss.ac.cn</email></corresp></author-notes><pub-date pub-type="epub"><day>09</day><month>12</month><year>2015</year></pub-date><volume>05</volume><issue>01</issue><fpage>41</fpage><lpage>44</lpage><permissions><copyright-statement>&#169; Copyright  2014 by authors and Scientific Research Publishing Inc. </copyright-statement><copyright-year>2014</copyright-year><license><license-p>This work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution International License (CC BY). http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/</license-p></license></permissions><abstract><p>
 
 
  本文解决了参考文献[1]中提出的一个公开问题，用初等方法确定了一个正定不等式成立的最佳参数值。
   In this paper, we solved an open problem proposed in [1]. We get a sharp parameter value of a positive definite inequality by elementary method.
 
</p></abstract><kwd-group><kwd>最佳参数，正定，不等式, Sharp Parameter Value</kwd><kwd> Positive Definite</kwd><kwd> Inequality</kwd></kwd-group></article-meta></front><body><sec id="s1"><title>一个正定不等式的最佳参数<sup> </sup></title><p>冯贝叶</p><p>中国科学院应用数学研究所，北京</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.16966-formula527"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x6_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>收稿日期：2016年1月30日；录用日期：2016年2月20日；发布日期：2016年2月23日</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.16966-formula528"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x7_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula></sec><sec id="s2"><title>摘 要</title><p>本文解决了参考文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.16966-ref1">1</xref>] 中提出的一个公开问题，用初等方法确定了一个正定不等式成立的最佳参数值。</p><p>关键词 :最佳参数，正定，不等式</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.16966-formula529"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x8_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>多项式的正定性条件及正定多项式是否能表示成平方和的问题是一个和Hilbert 17问题有关的有趣而又古老的问题，见 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.16966-ref1">1</xref>] - [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.16966-ref5">5</xref>] 。</p><p>设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x9_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x10_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。Murray Marshall在 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.16966-ref1">1</xref>] 中用微积分方法证明了如下断言：“Claim 1. When<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x11_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>, <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x12_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>on<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x13_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>”。然后他做了一个注记；“<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x14_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>is <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x15_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula> on <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x16_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula> when <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x17_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula> is ‘large enough’. Claim 1. shows that <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x18_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula> is ‘large enough’ in this sense. There is no claim that <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x19_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula> is in any way optimal”。本文用初等方法证明了在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x20_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中使这一不等式成立的最佳参数是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x21_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>显然我们有<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x22_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，因此我们只需对<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x23_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的情况证明这一不等式成立即可。</p><p>引理1. 当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x24_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时有<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x25_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p>证明：由计算直接得出引理1成立。</p><p>引理2.<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x26_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，等号仅在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x27_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时成立。</p><p>证明：从等式</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.16966-formula530"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x28_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>可知引理2成立。</p><p>引理3.<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x29_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，等号仅在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x30_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时成立</p><p>证明：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.16966-formula531"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x31_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.16966-formula532"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x32_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.16966-formula533"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x33_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x34_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>因此不等式<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x35_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>等价于不等式<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x36_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，从引理2即得引理3成立。</p><p>定理 在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x37_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x38_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，等号当且仅当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x39_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时成立，此外在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x40_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中使不等式<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x41_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>成立的最佳参数为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x42_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>证明。考虑以下两种情况</p><p>1)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x43_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>在这种情况下，设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x44_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，那么</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x45_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>要使上述不等式的等号成立，其充分必要条件是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x46_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x47_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>同时成立，但是易于验证，</p><p>这是不可能的，所以在这种情况下，上述不等式中的等号不可能成立。</p><p>2)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x48_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。在这种情况下，设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x49_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，那么</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x50_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>把上面的表达式看成是z的二次三项式，那么其判别式为</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x51_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>因此，这个二次三项式有两个实根<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x52_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，其中</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x53_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x54_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>从引理1和引理3可知<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x55_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，以及当且仅当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x56_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x57_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。因而</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x58_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>上述不等式中的等号当且仅当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x59_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时成立。</p><p>又设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x60_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是一个任意小的正常数，那么我们有</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x61_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>这就说明在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x62_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>上使<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x63_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>成立的最佳参数为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-2620240x64_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>这就完成了定理的证明。</p></sec><sec id="s3"><title>文章引用</title><p>冯贝叶. 一个正定不等式的最佳参数A Sharp Parameter Value of a Positive Definite Inequality[J]. 应用数学进展, 2016, 05(01): 41-44. http://dx.doi.org/10.12677/AAM.2016.51006</p></sec><sec id="s4"><title>参考文献 (Referen